OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThis morning will be dry with
OL,6,Fsunny spells. This afternoon will
OL,7,Fremain dry with some spells of
OL,8,Fsunshine. Brisk northerly wind along
OL,9,Fthe east coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,12,Fsome late sunshine. Then the rest of
OL,13,Fthe night will remain dry with some
OL,14,Flengthy clear periods. Cold with rural
OL,15,Ffrost.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FAll parts will have a dry day
OL,18,Fwith some good spells of sunshine.
OL,19,FLight winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
