OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FEarly
OL,6,Fshowery rain on Monday then dry and
OL,7,Fbright. A few early showers on Tuesday
OL,8,Fthen mainly dry and bright. Cool with
OL,9,Fwidespread showers on Wednesday.
